Build requirements:

1) TeXLive 2013 installed with support of Russian language, XeLaTeX, Tikz, biblatex, biber.
2) Both Windows and Linux hosts should be able to build

Build sequence:

1) cd metoda
2) xelatex main.tex
3) biber main
4) xelatex main.tex
5) xelatex main.tex

The result is in main.pdf.

